    {
      "name": "Bash",
      "args": {
        "command": "stm32 debug svd-path STM32L476RG",
        "description": "Resolve SVD file path for STM32L476RG"
      }
    }
  ],
  "final_text": "The SVD for the STM32L476RG resolves to:\n\n```\n/opt/st/stm32cubeide_2.1.1/plugins/com.st.stm32cube.ide.mcu.productdb.debug_2.2.400.202601091600/resources/cmsis/STMicroelectronics_CMSIS_SVD/STM32L476.svd\n```\n\nIt comes from the CubeIDE-bundled CMSIS SVD catalog (configured sources: `cubeide`, `stm32cubeclt`) \u2014 note the file is the family-level `STM32L476.svd`, which covers the RG variant."
}